# FFTSetupD

**Type Alias**

An opaque type that contains setup information for a given double-precision FFT transform.

## Declaration

```swift
typedef struct OpaqueFFTSetupD *FFTSetupD;
```

## Discussion

A setup object can be allocated with [doc://com.apple.accelerate/documentation/Accelerate/vDSP_create_fftsetupD] and destroyed with [doc://com.apple.accelerate/documentation/Accelerate/vDSP_destroy_fftsetupD]. The setup object includes, among other things, precomputed tables used in computing an FFT of the specified size.
